  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE THE STATE BOARD OF HEALTH TO PROMULGATE RULES AND REGULATIONS TO ESTABLISH STANDARDS FOR A STATEWIDE OBSTETRICS SYSTEM OF CARE; TO SET THE STANDARDS FOR SUCH RULES; TO PROVIDE THAT THE STATE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH SHALL BE THE LEAD AGENCY FOR OBSTETRICS SYSTEM OF CARE DEVELOPMENT, IMPLEMENTATION AND MANAGEMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
